  1. Build WARs
  ./data/buildWar.sh
  ./patient/buildWar.sh
  ./doctor/buildWar.sh
  ./hospital/buildWar.sh

  2. Build Docker images
  docker build -t dg-data data/
  docker build -t dg-patient patient/
  docker build -t dg-doctor doctor/
  docker build -t dg-hospital hospital/

  3. Run docker compose
  docker compose up
  Or in the background:
  docker compose up -d

  4. Shut down and clean everything

  Stop only (keeps DB data):
  docker compose down

  Stop + wipe the database volume (full reset):
  docker compose down -v

  Stop + wipe DB volume + remove built images:
  docker compose down -v
  docker rmi dg-data dg-patient

Running:
  - Patient → http://localhost:8888/patient
  - Doctor → http://localhost:8081/doctor
  - Hospital → http://localhost:8082/hospital
